    "The median under-reporting rate across studies was 94% with an interquartile range of 82-98%, with no significant difference in medians between general practice and hospital studies.",
    "However, general practice studies indicated a higher median under-reporting rate for all ADRs versus more serious/severe ADRs, while hospital studies consistently showed high medians for serious/severe ADRs.",
    "Studies of specific serious/severe ADR-drug combinations had a lower but still high median under-reporting rate of 85%.",
